                    <h4 onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">Do flowers come in a vase?</h4>
                    <p>Please be informed that not all the products come in a vase and we do not have options to change hand bouquets into a vase arrangement at the moment. Only products pictured to be in a vase come with it.  
